# High-End Visuals and Motion

- Implement interactive image galleries with polished transitions, hover states, and keyboard support.
- Use Framer Motion for smooth, purposeful animations that support storytelling and conversion.
- Animate with restraint: prioritize clarity, performance, and reduced-motion accessibility.
- Use lazy loading, responsive image sizing, and optimized media handling for visual-heavy pages.
- Favor micro-interactions that communicate state and elevate perceived quality.
